::Autofire::

"I am on my way," Autofire responds, speeding up toward Megatron. He
wasn't too far away, and he would be there in a minute or two.




--- In nbwrpg@y..., "rAuq" <rauq@t...> wrote:
> ::Astroblast/Drag Strip::
> 
> Drag Strip arrives shortly after Speedbreaker and lands beside him, 
>  "Lord Megatron, Drag Strip reporting,"
> 
> Astroblast complies. He immediately opens a commlink to 
> Autofire, "Autofire, Megatron wants you here, now. I suggest you 
> get here kinda fast, he's already kinda mad that you pulled out 
> before he could get there." He terminates the commlink, and his 
> speakers come online, "Megatron, I need to get repaired if you 
> intend to do any more long range transport."
